{"tid":1463964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政疪","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:00:30.000Z","uid":171669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"667107ad606654e7114f0b144b88889df1933cf6","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"#不割蓆 #p牌仔一個<br />\n我已經唔知道我開呢個po岩唔岩，但我真係好擔心每一個企出黎前線既香港人。<br />\n原屬醫護界既我，每日睇到新聞都好心痛⋯⋯812我係機場喊左出黎⋯⋯我擔心大家會受傷，亦擔心大家心靈，mental health會受創。<br />\n依家好多人被補，審判日期亦都係快到不可理喻。我希望大家參考一下呢個新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-48363312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-48363312&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=e18f78f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-48363312&h=cf4870d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-48363312</a><br />\n入面話：黃台仰在德國接受美國《華爾街日報》訪問時說，他是在「沒有選擇」的情況下才在當地申請庇護，形容香港的情況「越來越黑暗」。「我們現在必須在外部為香港而戰。」<br />\n好想幫大家出盡最大既力去抗爭⋯⋯<br />\n可唔可以幫被補既人申請政疪？<br />\n以個人所知，除左德國外，歐美澳都會政疪。而今年，加拿大亦開放左108萬個移民位，新加坡，台灣亦都會大量吸納。我絕非叫各位離家離港！因為縱使身在何方，大家都心繫香港！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申利：想幫被警犬屈嘅義士，想幫穿眼醫護，想幫香港人"},{"pid":"eb8caf578e6e73425b127965eb0c079b024260b7","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6257b047e58272b14b993754f118a2097c58d915","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"救港"},{"pid":"bf2c2b8559bdefd6757d99c15ea8471f8a0e093a","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"救義士"},{"pid":"02232c25ecc9c30493330211d55bf3c40be6fb50","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"救穿眼女護"},{"pid":"3f4e64d1499ccea10c46acef6238f91ba6fbf831","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"救被警人渣打既學生"},{"pid":"d144a80055edd5b597d8204c26df0f95e553ec15","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"求大家都有一顆憐憫之心，救救學生，救救下一代，救救義士！"},{"pid":"ce847275f25972b85d7d43ada8df02ab2a82f332","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"求下大家幫下佢地！佢地用自己將來，用自己人生，救緊你地下一代！"},{"pid":"440e11e458f2e980431eae9f014f4adac63695c6","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"求幫推！求下大家！依家嘈交無用架！<br />\n救得一個得一個！大家手牽手撐下去！"},{"pid":"d316c9d63c7c5c5f28d5f21eec45abd5e6857478","tid":1463964,"uid":171669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}